/// Returns usage documentation for the udf.adaptfy.timeintellgence library.
function 'udf.adaptfy.timeintellgence.About' =
		() =>
		VAR LineBreak = UNICHAR ( 10 )
		RETURN
		    "💡 Library:   udf.adaptfy.timeintellgence"   & LineBreak &
		    "🧑 Author:    Adaptfy"                         & LineBreak &
		    "📦 Version:   0.1.0"                           & LineBreak &
		    "⚖️  License:   Unspecified"                      & LineBreak &
